HEADWORD: Full house
<hw>Full house</hw>. <fld>(Poker)</fld> <def>A hand containing three of
a kind and a pair, as three kings and two tens. It ranks above a flush
and below four of a kind.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fulling</ent>⟦br⟧
